OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1778785871
OL,3,CJersey funds seized after #29 million
OL,4,Cglobal bribery racket uncovered
OL,6,FA Brazilian businessman who laundered
OL,7,Fcriminal funds through a complex
OL,8,Ffinancial network has been ordered to
OL,9,Fgive up more than #700,000 from Jersey
OL,10,Fbank accounts.
OL,12,FExpedito Machado deposited the tainted
OL,13,Fmoney in the Channel Islands as part
OL,14,Fof an international bribery network
OL,15,Frun by his father, Jose Sergio de
OL,16,FOliveria Machado, who was the Chief
OL,17,FExecutive of Brazil's largest oil and
OL,18,Fgas transport company Transpetro.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
