FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1778785871
OL,3,CJersey funds seized after #29 million
OL,4,Cglobal bribery racket uncovered
OL,6,FJose had received more than #29
OL,7,Fmillion from Brazilian, Greek, German
OL,8,Fand Norwegian businesses to secure
OL,9,Fshipping contracts and services with
OL,10,Fhis firm.
OL,12,FThe large-scale corruption was
OL,13,Funcovered by Brazilian authorities in
OL,14,Fan investigation called Operacao Lava
OL,15,FJato - or Operation Car Wash.
OL,26,@vD@^{qvD@_tp
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1778785871
OL,3,CJersey funds seized after #29 million
OL,4,Cglobal bribery racket uncovered
OL,6,FExpedito laundered some of the bribe
OL,7,Fmoney paid to his father between 2007
OL,8,Fand 2013 through Switzerland and four
OL,9,FJersey trusts, disguising the payments
OL,10,Fas legitimate commercial bank
OL,11,Ftransfers.
OL,13,FThese trusts were then used to finance
OL,14,Fcompanies that would buy property in
OL,15,Fthe UK.
OL,17,FThe Economic Crime and Confiscation
OL,18,FUnit (ECCU) of Jersey's Law Officers'
OL,19,FDepartment proved the trail back to
OL,20,Fthe tainted money.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1778785871
OL,3,CJersey funds seized after #29 million
OL,4,Cglobal bribery racket uncovered
OL,6,FExpedito has already pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fmoney laundering offences in Brazil
OL,8,Fand Switzerland, while confirming the
OL,9,Ffundamental facts of Jersey's case to
OL,10,Fthe Attorney General Matthew Jowitt KC
OL,11,Fin an affidavit.
OL,13,FThe island's chief prosecutor formally
OL,14,Fapplied to the Royal Court for a
OL,15,FForfeiture of Assets order which has
OL,16,Fbeen granted, meaning a total of
OL,17,F#725,783 will be seized.
OL,19,FThe Jersey authorities intend to
OL,20,Freturn the funds to the Brazilian
OL,21,Fauthorities, minus legal costs.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
