OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1778785871
OL,3,CJersey funds seized after #29 million
OL,4,Cglobal bribery racket uncovered
OL,6,FMr Jowitt explains: "The Royal Court's
OL,7,Forder concludes a complex and long-
OL,8,Frunning asset forfeiture investigation
OL,9,Fby ECCU.
OL,11,F"This is further evidence that the
OL,12,F2018 Forfeiture Law is a vital tool in
OL,13,Frecovering the proceeds of corruption
OL,14,Fand restoring that money to victims of
OL,15,Finternational financial crime."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
